Merge pull request #12 from sobolevn/patch-1

Updates README.rst with svg badge

Merge pull request #8 from adamchainz/fix_config_parse_for_no-accept-encodings

Fix no-accept-encodings to work in config files

Fix no-accept-encodings to work in config files

I found with flake8 3.0.4 if I have bare `no-accept-encodings` in my config file, it just crashes, and it needs `no-accept-encodings = something` in the file. Then the `parse_from_config` flag is required on the option to indicate that as a flag it should indeed be parsed.

Merge pull request #9 from adamchainz/drop_python_2.6

Drop Python 2.6 compatibility

Drop Python 2.6 compatibility

As noted in #8 flake8 3.0.0+ doesn't support it, so this plugin shouldn't either. Fixes build.
Fix does not work with flake8-3.0
